{"ja434:0.1":"Jataka ","ja434:0.2":"Navakanipata ","ja434:0.3":"Gijjhavagga ","ja434:0.4":"8. Cakkavakajataka ","ja434:1.1":"“Kasayavatthe sakune vadami, ","ja434:1.2":"Duve duve nandamane carante; ","ja434:1.3":"Kam andajam andaja manusesu, ","ja434:1.4":"Jatim pasamsanti tadingha brutha”. ","ja434:2.1":"“Amhe manussesu manussahimsa, ","ja434:2.2":"Anubbate cakkavake vadanti; ","ja434:2.3":"Kalyanabhavamhe dijesu sammata, ","ja434:2.4":"Abhirupa vicarama annave”. ","ja434:2.5":"(…) ","ja434:3.1":"“Kim annave kani phalani bhunje, ","ja434:3.2":"Mamsam kuto khadatha cakkavaka; ","ja434:3.3":"Kim bhojanam bhunjatha vo anoma, ","ja434:3.4":"Balanca vanno ca anapparupa”. ","ja434:4.1":"“Na annave santi phalani dhanka, ","ja434:4.2":"Mamsam kuto khaditum cakkavake; ","ja434:4.3":"Sevalabhakkhamha apanabhojana, ","ja434:4.4":"Na ghasahetupi karoma papam”. ","ja434:5.1":"“Na me idam ruccati cakkavaka, ","ja434:5.2":"Asmim bhave bhojanasannikaso; ","ja434:5.3":"Ahosi pubbe tato me annatha, ","ja434:5.4":"Icceva me vimati ettha jata. ","ja434:6.1":"Ahampi mamsani phalani bhunje, ","ja434:6.2":"Annani ca loniyateliyani; ","ja434:6.3":"Rasam manussesu labhami bhottum, ","ja434:6.4":"Surova sangamamukham vijetva; ","ja434:6.5":"Na ca me tadiso vanno, ","ja434:6.6":"Cakkavaka yatha tava”. ","ja434:7.1":"“Asuddhabhakkhosi khananupati, ","ja434:7.2":"Kicchena te labbhati annapanam; ","ja434:7.3":"Na tussasi rukkhaphalehi dhanka, ","ja434:7.4":"Mamsani va yani susanamajjhe. ","ja434:8.1":"Yo sahasena adhigamma bhoge, ","ja434:8.2":"Paribhunjati dhanka khananupati; ","ja434:8.3":"Tato upakkosati nam sabhavo, ","ja434:8.4":"Upakkuttho vannabalam jahati. ","ja434:9.1":"Appampi ce nibbutim bhunjati yadi, ","ja434:9.2":"Asahasena aparupaghati; ","ja434:9.3":"Balanca vanno ca tadassa hoti, ","ja434:9.4":"Na hi sabbo aharamayena vanno”ti. ","ja434:10.1":"Cakkavakajatakam atthamam. "}